816
00:57:49,540 --> 00:57:51,329
We'll meet tomorrow evening.

817
00:57:51,330 --> 00:57:54,150
But what if I wanted to see you right now?

818
00:57:55,030 --> 00:57:56,930
Try to hold on.

819
00:57:58,810 --> 00:58:02,119
I guess you don't miss me that much.

820
00:58:02,120 --> 00:58:03,409
You have things to do tomorrow.

821
00:58:03,410 --> 00:58:06,419
I don't want you to struggle because of me.

822
00:58:06,420 --> 00:58:09,170
Of course I miss you too.

823
00:58:12,420 --> 00:58:15,379
There's a comic book I want to read right now.

824
00:58:15,380 --> 00:58:17,659
The first copy was released in 1996.

825
00:58:17,660 --> 00:58:19,879
You can't even find it on the internet.

826
00:58:19,880 --> 00:58:21,619
- Excuse me? - I can't stand it anymore.

827
00:58:21,620 --> 00:58:23,359
I need to read it now.

828
00:58:23,360 --> 00:58:26,780
But at your house.

829
00:58:27,880 --> 00:58:29,059
I'll be right there.

830
00:58:29,060 --> 00:58:31,129
It's not you.

831
00:58:31,130 --> 00:58:33,620
I'm getting my comic book.

832
00:58:36,100 --> 00:58:38,789
Okay. I'll find it for you.

833
00:58:38,790 --> 00:58:40,330
Okay.

834
00:58:59,240 --> 00:59:01,610
What a huge head.

835
00:59:14,600 --> 00:59:17,230
[Black Dragon]

836
00:59:27,030 --> 00:59:29,619
He acted as if he didn't like it.

837
00:59:29,620 --> 00:59:32,200
But he kept it in a very precious way.

838
00:59:33,360 --> 00:59:35,860
Is she a little ugly?

839
00:59:41,300 --> 00:59:45,270
Where might the comic book be?

840
01:00:31,130 --> 01:00:32,800
Su Jeong.

841
01:00:37,450 --> 01:00:40,200
Why are you out? I told you to come out when I called.

842
01:00:41,560 --> 01:00:43,880
Did you miss me a lot?

843
01:00:56,480 --> 01:01:00,879
You're the only one who can set the Black Dragon free.

844
01:01:00,880 --> 01:01:04,389
Please give me love...

845
01:01:04,390 --> 01:01:06,270
And freedom.

846
01:01:14,030 --> 01:01:15,760
This is why...

847
01:01:25,000 --> 01:01:27,240
You're the Black Dragon, aren't you?

848
01:01:48,360 --> 01:01:51,810
[My Dearest Enemy]

849
01:01:52,400 --> 01:01:55,200
[Thank you to Yoon Park for his special participation]

850
01:02:19,730 --> 01:02:22,229
I think I was very lonely again.

851
01:02:22,230 --> 01:02:24,409
You said you liked me too.

852
01:02:24,410 --> 01:02:27,049
I didn't know who he was at the time.

853
01:02:27,050 --> 01:02:28,759
I am sad.

854
01:02:28,760 --> 01:02:30,819
Could you be a little gentler with me?

855
01:02:30,820 --> 01:02:34,459
There was an article on the office worker website this morning.

856
01:02:34,460 --> 01:02:37,079
I heard that Team Leader Baek is going to marry the director.

857
01:02:37,080 --> 01:02:38,969
- Is this true? - Baek Su Jeong.

858
01:02:38,970 --> 01:02:41,439
Quietly remove him from the company.

859
01:02:41,440 --> 01:02:43,819
It's not easy. It was expected.

860
01:02:43,820 --> 01:02:46,380
So, let's give up.